response.overview: The Vietnamese Loas is probably the most ideal waitress to serve Harry's oriental dish during the opening of the Excuse Me Club... or should she serve him first? All of Harry's friends are celebrating Natacha's wedding in Antwerp, so hopefully the voluptuous Leentje will comfort him! On the same evening, Harry is horny again and rips open the slim, horny Lien. But when he returns to Rotterdam the next day, it's the dark-haired Nina who really enjoys the load! And then the Excuse Me Club opens...
response.title: Excuse Me... 25
